10 ounce Maple Pork Breakfast Sausage

STOVETOP: Heat a drizzle of oil in a large pan over medium-high heat. Add sausage and cook, turning occasionally, until browned all over and cooked through, 8-12 minutes.

OVEN: Preheat oven to 425 degrees. Place sausage on a baking sheet. Roast until browned and cooked through, 18-20 minutes.